                <note rend="inline" type="source">713.1311/264a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lane</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-03-01T14:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 1, 1934—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>18. Please inquire informally of President Sacasa whether he has selected
                    delegates to the Central American Conference and what preparations for it are
                    being made in Nicaragua.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
